  "prompt": "What are some interesting questions to ask yourself?",
  "response": "Here are some thought-provoking questions to ask yourself:\n\n1. Personal Growth\n- What are my core values?\n- Am I living authentically?\n- What fears are holding me back?\n- What would I do if I wasn't afraid?\n\n2. Self-Reflection\n- What makes me truly happy?\n- What have I learned about myself in the past year?\n- What would my ideal day look like?\n- What am I most proud of?\n\n3. Future Planning\n- Where do I want to be in 5 years?\n- What skills do I want to develop?\n- What legacy do I want to leave?\n- What would I do if money wasn't a concern?\n\n4. Philosophical Questions\n- What does success mean to me?\n- Am I making a positive difference in the world?\n- What gives my life meaning?\n- How do I define happiness?\n\n5. Emotional Intelligence\n- What triggers my strongest emotions?\n- How do I handle stress?\n- What relationships truly matter to me?\n- How can I be more compassionate?\n\n6. Creative Exploration\n- What haven't I tried that I'm curious about?\n- What would I do if I knew I couldn't fail?\n- What does creativity mean to me?\n\nThese questions can lead to deep personal insights and self-understanding.",
